<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM3.2.2">
<l>kāyō ṭunīṭu kaṉiyuṇ ṭuvīcu kaṭuṅkāl nukarntu neṭuṅkā lamaintu</l>
<l>tīyō ṭuniṉṟu tavañcey yavēṇṭā tirumār paṉaiccin taiyuḷvait tumeṉpīr</l>
<l>vāyō tuvētam malikiṉ ṟatolcīr maṟaiyā ḷarnāḷum muṟaiyāl vaḷartta</l>
<l>tīyōṅ kavōṅkap pukaḻōṅ kutillait tiruccit rakūṭam ceṉṟucēr miṉkaḷē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You who say, ‘We keep in mind the one with Tiru at his chest,’</l>
<l rend="indent">it is not necessary to do penance,</l>
<l>Staying with the five fires for long periods, eating overripe fruit with unripe,</l>
<l rend="indent">suffering the fierce winds which buffet!</l>
<l>Go and gather at Tiruccitrakūṭam in Tillai, where fame rises</l>
<l rend="indent">since the flames continue to rise,</l>
<l>Which Vedic experts of ancient fame, who broadcast the Vedas</l>
<l rend="indent">chanted orally, nurture daily according to the rules,</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
